msgstr "Ceangailte ri Last.fm"

#: src/widgets/window.vala:299
msgid "Discover 30,000+ verified radio stations from around the world"
msgstr ""
"Lorg còrr is 30,000 stèisean rèidio dearbhte bho air feadh an t-saoghail"

