msgid "No Favourites"
msgstr "Gun annsachdan"

#: src/widgets/favourites_page.vala:26
msgid "Star stations while browsing to add them here"
msgstr ""
"Cuir rionnag air stèiseanan fhad 's a bhios tu a' brabhsadh gus an cur ris "
